# .clang-tidy for Simple-XX/SimpleRenderer.

---
Checks: '-*,\
  bugprone-*,\
  clang-analyzer-*,\
  cppcoreguidelines-*,\
  hicpp-*,\
  llvm-*,\
  misc-*
  modernize-*,\
  performance-*,\
  portability-*,\
  readability-*,\
  -cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-reinterpret-cast'
HeaderFilterRegex: '^${sourceDir}/src'
AnalyzeTemporaryDtors: true
...
